spec_data.Name: perl-Math-Expression-Evaluator
spec_data.Description:
Math::Expression::Evaluator is a parser, compiler and interpreter for
mathematical expressions. It can handle normal arithmetic (including
powers wit ^ or **), built-in functions like sin() and variables.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:12:09 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Parses, compiles and evaluates mathematics expressions
